<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Raspadinha Especial</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif; text-align: center; background-color: #fdfdfd; padding: 20px; color: #333; }
        h1 { color: #ff5d00; }
        .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 100px); gap: 15px; justify-content: center; margin: 30px auto; max-width: 350px; }
        .cell { 
            width: 100px; height: 100px; background-color: #bdc3c7; 
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; 
            cursor: pointer; font-size: 28px; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            transition: all 0.2s; position: relative; overflow: hidden;
        }
        .cell:hover { background-color: #aab2b7; transform: scale(1.05); }
        .revealed { background-color: #fff; border: 2px solid #ff5d00; transform: scale(1) !important; box-shadow: none; }
        .logo { width: 80%; height: auto; display: none; pointer-events: none; }
        .revealed .logo { display: block; }
        .revealed .num { display: none; }
        
        #message { 
            margin: 30px auto; max-width: 500px; display: none; 
            padding: 25px; border: 3px solid #ff5d00; border-radius: 20px;
            background-color: #fff2e6; animation: pop 0.5s ease;
        }
        @keyframes pop { 0% { transform: scale(0.8); } 100% { transform: scale(1); } }
        button { background: #ff5d00; color: white; border: none; padding: 12px 25px; border-radius: 25px; font-weight: bold; cursor: pointer; margin-top: 15px; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <h1>Tenta a tua sorte! 🍀</h1>
    <p>Escolhe <b>3 números</b> para raspar e ganhar o teu prémio:</p>

    <div class="grid" id="grid">
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">1</span><img src="https://logodownload.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/repsol-logo-0.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">2</span><img src="https://logodownload.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/repsol-logo-0.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">3</span><img src="https://logodownload.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/repsol-logo-0.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">4</span><img src="https://logodownload.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/repsol-logo-0.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">5</span><img src="https://logodownload.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/repsol-logo-0.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">6</span><img src="https://logodownload.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/repsol-logo-0.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">7</span><img src="https://logodownload.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/repsol-logo-0.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">8</span><img src="https://logodownload.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/repsol-logo-0.png" class="logo"></div>
        <div class="cell" onclick="reveal(this)"><span class="num">9</span><img src="https://logodownload.org/wp-content/uploads/2014/09/repsol-logo-0.png" class="logo"></div>
    </div>

    <div id="message">
        <h2 style="margin-top:0;">🎉 PARABÉNS! 🎉</h2>
        <p style="font-size: 1.2em;">Acabaste de ganhar a obrigatoriedade de fazer um contrato <b>Repsol</b> hoje!</p>
        <button onclick="window.location.reload()">Aceitar Prémio</button>
    </div>

    <script>
        let count = 0;
        function reveal(element) {
            if (!element.classList.contains('revealed') && count < 3) {
                element.classList.add('revealed');
                count++;

                if (count === 3) {
                    setTimeout(() => {
                        document.getElementById('message').style.display = 'block';
                        document.getElementById('grid').style.pointerEvents = 'none'; 
                    }, 600);
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
